grep print lines included a serching word

Usage:
 ./my_grep.rb [OPTIONS] PATTERN FILES

OPTIONS:
'-A3' -print lines around the printing line
'-e'  -use regular expression
'-R'  -search recursively in directories
'-z'  -parsing gzipped files
'-h'  -print help

PATTERN:
any word or regular expression in case option '-e'

FILES
may include directories in case option '-R'
